The Teleport MWI Terraform provider generates short-lived credentials using
Teleport Machine & Workload Identity (MWI) that can be used to grant other
Terraform providers access to resources.

For example, you can use the Teleport MWI Terraform provider to grant the
Kubernetes Terraform provider access to a Kubernetes cluster.

To manage the configuration of Teleport itself, use the [Teleport Terraform
Provider instead](../terraform-provider/terraform-provider.mdx).

